---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Surf Deeper" description="Surf deeper. Learn more. Share what you know. A community-driven hub for surfers of all levels.">
  <header class="homepage-header">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <svg class="wave-logo" viewBox="0 0 200 120" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs>
          <linearGradient id="waveGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
            <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#00ff88;stop-opacity:1" />
            <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#00cc6a;stop-opacity:1" />
          </linearGradient>
        </defs>
        <path d="M20,80 Q40,20 80,40 Q120,60 160,30 Q180,20 200,50 L200,120 L0,120 Z" fill="url(#waveGradient)" />
        <path d="M20,90 Q50,50 90,70 Q130,90 170,60 Q190,50 200,80 L200,120 L0,120 Z" fill="#00cc6a" opacity="0.8" />
        <path d="M20,100 Q60,70 100,90 Q140,110 180,80 Q200,70 200,100 L200,120 L0,120 Z" fill="#00aa55" opacity="0.6" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Surf Deeper</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Surf deeper. Learn more. Share what you know.</p>
  </header>

      <section class="about">
        <h2>About</h2>
        <p>Explore the ocean, master the waves, and share your knowledge.</p>
        <p>Coming soon: a community-driven hub for surfers of all levels — from first waves to advanced lines. Learn techniques, discover surf spots, and contribute your own guides.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="features">
        <h2>What You'll Find Here:</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Technique Library:</strong> Step-by-step tips, from paddling efficiently to riding the pocket.</li>
          <li><strong>Spot Guides:</strong> Maps, local insights, tide charts, and hazards contributed by the community.</li>
          <li><strong>Open Contribution:</strong> Share your own tips, maps, and stories with fellow surfers.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="why-different">
        <h2>Why It's Different:</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Techniques broken down with nuance and clarity, so you can improve safely</li>
          <li>Open-source, free, and community-driven</li>
          <li>Focused on learning and sharing, not profit</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="pullquote">
        <blockquote>
          <p>“Before diving into wave types, note the striking similarity between ocean waves, hurricanes, and even galaxies. Spirals are nature’s way of channeling energy efficiently. Waves curl, roll, and crash along these spirals, revealing patterns that are physical, mathematical, and profoundly beautiful.”</p>
        </blockquote>
        <p class="pullquote-cta">
          <a href="/how-to/types-of-waves#spirals-in-motion">Explore the spiral connection →</a>
        </p>
      </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .homepage-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .logo-container {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .wave-logo {
    width: 120px;
    height: 72px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: block;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 8px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.3));
  }
  
  .homepage-header h1 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  
  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: #00ff88;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  
  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  h2 {
    color: #00ff88;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #00ff88;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  
  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: #00ff88;
  }
  
  
  strong {
    color: #00ff88;
  }
  
  p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #00ff88;
  }

  .pullquote {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    background-color: #1e293b;
    border: 2px solid #334155;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pullquote blockquote {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
    padding-left: 1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid #00ff88;
  }

  .pullquote p {
    color: #00ff88;
  }

  .pullquote-cta a {
    color: #00ff88;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }
</style>
